{"tid":1509494,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[必也正名] 由今日開始，將「黑警」改為「老鼠」","createTime":"2019-08-27T00:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T01:46:41.000Z","uid":158404,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2928d6c5f9be2313c271ed5811bed1566f8ac335","tid":1509494,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:48:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">知唔知你用<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警</span></span><br />\n一個字係<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警</span></span><br />\n比人感覺佢地仲係<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警察</span></span><br />\n仲係權威一方<br />\n只係有部份黑咗<br />\n唔能夠破壞佢地形象<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然佢地叫我地為曱甴<br />\n我地將會叫佢地<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老鼠</span></span><br />\n一個純無權威嘅生物<br />\n以其人之道還治其人之身<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老鼠</span></span>嘅破壞力將會大過<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但要求大家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">香港警察 知法犯法</span></span><br />\n亦唔岩用<br />\n令人仲覺得佢地有法嘅概念<br />\n係執法一方<br />\n應該轉用<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察 強姦謀殺</span></span><br />\n先可以將佢地往死裏推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最後，應承我，一世都唔原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"b79c64c6fa6be83dab0045c06561f3032a217ef7","tid":1509494,"uid":4798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:48:42.000Z","msg":"推！重要！"},{"pid":